formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) BU permission is received on 08/03/2022 from A.M.C. for the project, however Guj RERA portal is not allowing to input BU permission date greater than project end date i.e. 31/12/2018, hence BU permission date is mentioned as 31/12/2018 in Form-1 details as the Q-E is being submitted as per authority order.

2) The project was completed and possession for most of the units were given to allottees between 2010 to 2014. Hence, details of KYC and mobile number of Allottees as required in Form-3 Annexure are not available with the promoter and not possible to obtain now as the units were sold even before RERA Act was commenced, hence we have mentioned dummy numbers in Form-3 Annexure since Guj RERA portal does not accept blank details in KYC and Mobile number details.
